{"tid":905801,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[近朱者赤] IU媽媽超暖 「票價三分之一拿來逆應援」","createTime":"2018-11-17T12:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T06:44:53.000Z","uid":34643,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0c0c6d5a70ffbad5532950c4dbb342eb1e8080","tid":905801,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣歌手IU在2018年迎來出道十週年，17日、18日將在首爾展開演唱會巡演。向來寵粉絲的她，就連媽媽也是暖女。一入場粉絲就被「超暖逆應援」感動得不行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/WelloffDownrightAsiaticmouflon-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FWelloffDownrightAsiaticmouflon-size_restricted.gif&h=fbd3e1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU演唱會會祭出「暖舉」超有愛。（圖／華納提供）<br />\n<br />\nIU的10週年巡迴演唱會《2018 IU 10th Anniversary Tour Concert &lt;이지금 dlwlrma&gt; 》17日在奧林匹克體操競技場開唱。由於當日首爾只有6度低溫，IU的媽媽擔心場館座椅硬又涼，特別自掏腰包準備了座墊，寵粉行徑讓粉絲感動的說：「連偶像的媽媽都暖，一張票才7萬韓元（約台幣1906元），這個坐墊就要2萬了！（約544元）」幾乎是票價的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3701/d3701161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3701%2Fd3701161.jpg&h=aa9f69bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU的媽媽為粉絲在演唱會準備座墊。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3701/d3701160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3701%2Fd3701160.jpg&h=66356921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU的媽媽為粉絲在演唱會準備座墊。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\nIU疼愛粉絲不是第一次，這場演唱會開賣前，公司就祭出超嚴厲手段，只要是用「與票面價格明顯差價」轉賣者，無論是在二手票券平台，或是個人SNS平台（如臉書、推特等），皆會被認為是「不正當交易」，不但當天無法入場，也會被取消會員資格，維護粉絲的行為被讚「超帥氣」。而這場演唱會嘉賓也請到當紅女團TWICE，備受歌迷期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5549eaf091048c04dd1f1ddb017a4af4447bed","tid":905801,"uid":177955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"知恩者甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e366dbe2cd1e9c946cf0a6a6c9e86170ecd8a0","tid":905801,"uid":216704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"香港都有D特別野就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95caca870406a088733c9838719eb918523ad67f","tid":905801,"uid":37773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"我愛iu愛我"},{"pid":"5cb5f5180bd62edfb2a27f17ab81e55d39997337","tid":905801,"uid":87338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18098483a76a3f2e8e47dba003d880dd4261554","tid":905801,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e366dbe2cd1e9c946cf0a6a6c9e86170ecd8a0","tid":905801,"uid":216704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"香港都有D特別野就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401013d3806ff7284506b35bb98f664222731735","tid":905801,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗報咁大數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c436b447f1fc59336b258a8d4702abb79712693a","tid":905801,"uid":61130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"洗鬼咁貴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8cb530da488d701153b1d48ae4b7c91803801d","tid":905801,"uid":202653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/